last_episode_to_air.name: A Good Man
last_episode_to_air.overview: Gray discovers unlikely allies as he risks it all for revenge. The Tongais level up their operation, but face an unforeseen obstacle.

name: Parish
overview: Gray Parish is a good man with a troubled past who gave up his life of crime for life as a family man. But when his son is violently murdered, old habits return, sending him on a relentless quest with moral intentions and dangerous consequences.
tagline: The wrong way is the only way out.

episodes.name: Pilot
episodes.overview: Desperate to support his family, Gray returns to his criminal roots for one last job. But after things go sideways, Gray can't walk away. The only way out is through.

episodes.name: Blood in the Water
episodes.overview: Gray and Colin clash over a big clean up. Gray dodges his family's growing suspicion. The Tongais pursue new business.

episodes.name: Sanctuary
episodes.overview: Cornered, Gray's allegiance to Horse is put to the ultimate test. The Parish and Tongai families search for their missing loved ones. The Tongais gather intel on their adversary.

episodes.name: Impimpi
episodes.overview: When Anton, an old colleague, learns Gray is working with the Tongais, he forces Gray to choose: his family or Horse. Rose and Makayla work together to survive. Horse searches for a traitor.

episodes.name: Kumba
episodes.overview: Gray and his family face a terrible new normal and reckon with past trauma. Horse singles out the enemy within while expanding his business. He makes Gray an offer he can't refuse.
